                        <p class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">${fromCompany}</p>
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700">${fromName}</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">〒904-2142 沖縄県沖縄市登川3丁目31-10 L-STYLE A-2号室</p>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-700 pt-1 font-bold">TEL: ${fromTel} / FAX: ${fromFax}</p>
